'''''Oceanography and Marine Biology: An Annual Review''''' is an annual review of [[oceanography]] and [[marine biology]] that has been published since 1963. It was originally edited by Harold Barnes. It was originally published by [[Aberdeen University Press]] and [[Allen & Unwin]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://explore.bl.uk/primo_library/libweb/action/dlDisplay.do?vid=BLVU1&search_scope=LSCOP-ALL&docId=BLL01009544415&fn=permalink|title=Oceanography and marine biology.|date=7 November 1963|publisher=Allen and Unwin, Aberdeen University Press|accessdate=7 November 2018|via=Explore.bl.uk}}</ref> but is now published by [[CRC Press]], part of Taylor & Francis.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.crcpress.com/Oceanography-and-Marine-Biology---An-Annual-Review/book-series/CRCOCEMARBIO|title=Oceanography and Marine Biology - An Annual Review|website=Crcpress.com|accessdate=7 November 2018}}</ref> The 55th volume was published in 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.crcpress.com/Oceanography-and-Marine-Biology-An-Annual-Review-Volume-55/Hawkins-Evans-Dale-Firth-Hughes-Smith/p/book/9781138197862|title=Oceanography and Marine Biology: An Annual Review, Volume 55|date=10 November 2017|website=Crcpress.com|accessdate=7 November 2018}}</ref>

